{
  "id": 3,
  "title": "最大公因數",
  "difficulty": "Easy",
  "tags": ["數學", "遞迴"],
  "description": "<p>給定兩個正整數 <code>A</code> 和 <code>B</code>，請求出它們的<strong>最大公因數（GCD）</strong>。</p><p>你可以使用輾轉相除法（歐幾里得算法）來完成這題。</p>",
  "inputFormat": "<p>一行，包含兩個正整數 <code>A</code> 和 <code>B</code>，以空格分隔。</p>",
  "outputFormat": "<p>一行，輸出 <code>A</code> 和 <code>B</code> 的最大公因數。</p>",
  "constraints": "<ul><li>1 ≤ A, B ≤ 10<sup>9</sup></li></ul>",
  "timeLimit": 1,
  "memoryLimit": 256,
  "sampleInput": "12 8",
  "sampleOutput": "4",
  "testCases": [
    { "input": "12 8",        "output": "4"  },
    { "input": "100 75",      "output": "25" },
    { "input": "1 1",         "output": "1"  },
    { "input": "999999937 1", "output": "1"  },
    { "input": "48 36",       "output": "12" },
    { "input": "7 13",        "output": "1"  }
  ]
}
